 1. Project Overview

ConnectHub is a social networking web application where users can:

* Register and login
* Create posts with images
* Like and comment on posts
* Follow/unfollow users
* Send friend requests
* Receive notifications
* View personalized feeds
* Edit profiles
* Chat with friends (Advanced)

